photos.alt: A photo of a person walking uphill with a dog. The person wears glasses and looks in their phone. The dog is on a leash, and is a golden cocker spaniel. The path is narrow with a wall of green vegetation on the left, and a green wired fence with some vegetation on top on the right. The ground is covered with brown leaves, and in the background there is more out-of-focus vegetation visible.
